  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A titanium flightpack, assembled from technology stolen from the Sentinel horde. Its engines are precooled with a constant flow of pugneum and nitrogen, ensuring fuel-efficient and deadly silent operation.<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: do not unseal pugneum containment chamber without protective gear.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>使用从护卫部队窃取的技术组装的钛合金喷射背包。持续流动的普茵与氮对引擎部进行着预先冷却，一来确保了燃料效率，二来又能够确保装置在无声无息中顺畅运作。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：打开普茵储存室前请确保穿戴好防护用具。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>一種鈦金屬飛行背包，由從巡警軍團竊取而來的科技組裝而成。其引擎內部有搏與氮氣流不斷進行預冷，可有效使用燃料，且運作時寂靜無聲。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：請勿在未使用防護裝備的情況下開封搏容器槽。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
